net: stmmac: xgmac: Disable Flow Control when 1 or more queues are in AV

When in AVB mode we need to disable flow control to prevent MAC from
pausing in TX side.

Fixes: ec6ea8e3eee9 ("net: stmmac: Add CBS support in XGMAC2")
